# No Emojis or Non-Text Characters

## Code Standards
- **No emojis** in code, comments, or strings
- **No Unicode symbols** (arrows, bullets, checkmarks, etc.)
- **No special characters** beyond standard ASCII
- Use plain text descriptions instead of visual symbols

## Allowed Characters
- Standard ASCII letters, numbers, and punctuation
- Standard programming symbols: `{}[]()<>+-*/=!&|^~`
- Standard whitespace: spaces, tabs, newlines

